50 Cent supports Hitchin Ladies Rugby Club's naked calendar

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Members of a women's rugby club have spoken of their surprise after their fundraising calendar won the support of rap superstar 50 Cent.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The American musician shared an article about the Hitchin Ladies Rugby Club's naked calendar with the 37.9 million people who like his Facebook page.
The calendar is aimed at raising money to ensure the club continues to develop women's rugby in Hitchin.
Club members said they were "shocked" by the hip-hop star's interest.
